Journals & Magazines > Computing in Science & Engine... > Volume: 22 Issue: 3 
The Virtual Data Collaboratory: A Regional Cyberinfrastructure for Collaborative Data-Driven Research 
Publisher: IEEE 
Cite This 
PDF 
Manish Parashar ; Anthony Simonet ; Ivan Rodero ; Forough Ghahramani ; Grace Agnew ; Ron Jantz ; Vasant Honavar 
